node.text:
The Alpine Active Jacket features a 2-layers construction (Beretta Waterproof Breathable membrane and silent microfibre fabric), fully taped seams and a breathable lining. A number of functional inserts ensure protection against water, abrasion and wear. A highly technical garment designed for extreme cold conditions, that can be worn with a Beretta BIS second layer for further warmth and thermal insulation. 

#berettafw21

node.text:
Always by your side, especially when you’re in the harshest environments. The Thorn Resistant jacket can stand rain, abrasion, tears and cuts thanks to its innovative fabric construction. The @goretexeu membrane makes it waterproof and breathable, while the exterior fabric is specifically treated to be water repellent. A high density material and abrasion-resistant inserts in key areas guarantee you full protection from brambles and bushes. Available in green and EN20471 high visibility orange for added safety during your hunting outings. 

This jacket can be combined with the Thorn Resistant EVO pants. Check out our current Story to discover more.

#berettafw21

The Muker hunting jacket is specifically conceived for stalking or high seat, where you need to be 100% noise free at all times. Featuring a removable hood ensuring full visibility also when you’re moving, elastic inserts for unrivalled freedom of movement and a Z-Liner GORE membrane for waterproofness and breathability. A DWR (Durable Water Repellent) treatment on the outer fabric completes this high quality garment.

#berettafw21

Stay dry and cool in every condition: the innovative Polartec NeoShell® technology and the ventilation zips make the Ibex NeoShell® jacket breathable and waterproof. This outer shell features a noise-free stretch fabric, ideal for active hunting in open country or mountains. Abrasion resistant inserts on the shoulders improve durability while carrying a backpack. During cold weather this outer shell jacket can be combined with thermal layers to improve warmth retention and insulation. 

The Ibex NeoShell® pants complete the look - check out our Story to find out more.

The Butte Softshell jacket is a lightweight and breathable mid layer that can be worn also as a stand-alone, being particularly suitable for hunting or other outdoor activities on mountain terrain.
It features a BWR (Beretta Wind Resistant) membrane bonded with an internal soft microfleece, and a DWR (Durable Water Repellent) treatment, making it wind and water resistant but breathable at the same time. 

The Butte Softshell jacket can be combined with the Beretta 4 Way Stretch EVO or Bymark pants. Check out our Stories to discover more.

#berettafw21

Introducing the new Beretta Hunting / Outdoor Collection 2021-22.

The Field GTX® Anorak jacket is designed for hunting in open spaces, where you need to be silent and dry at all times. A high quality technical garment featuring elastic inserts in key areas to ensure freedom of movement, a waterproof and breathable GORE Z-liner membrane, ventilation zips under the armpits and doubled fabric on shoulders and elbows for increased durability. The outer shell features a DWR (Durable Water Repellent) treatment for extra protection. 

This garment can be combined with the Bymark Pants to create a full outfit. Check out our Stories to find out more.

#berettafw21

Introducing Beretta Ultraleggero, the lightest hunting shotgun: only 2,8kg for the 61cm/24” barrel version.

ultraleggero.beretta.com

node.text:
In addition to the classic single selective trigger, #BerettaUltraleggero is also available in an alternative configuration with a double single selective trigger: this particular mechanism features two single selective triggers, the front one allowing you to shoot the first barrel and then the second barrel, the back one shooting the second barrel and then the first barrel. This saves you time when in a split second you have to choose your adequate barrel, choke and cartridge combination. The result is a faster and more intuitive movement without losing concentration and precious time while aiming at your prey.

Visit our link in bio if you want to know more about Beretta Ultraleggero.

#getreadytogofar
#strengthmadelight

A high density material and abrasion-resistant inserts in key areas guarantee you full protection from brambles and bushes. Available in green and EN20471 high visibility orange for added safety during your hunting outings. 

This jacket can be combined with the Thorn Resistant EVO pants. Check out our current Story to discover more.
